{"tid":9289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：香港城邦論其實是英國式的政治理論","createTime":"2016-11-28T14:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T11:44:45.000Z","uid":2339,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b845423c37500abb00ff9d5b0953fc6d8a509326","tid":9289,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲：1984年，市政局議員曾經提出香港城邦自治論，雖然不及陳雲的《香港城邦論》（2011）精細及嚴謹，但畢竟是英雄所見略同！ <span style=\"color: red;\">1984年3月，市政局委任議員蘇偉澤（Walter M. Sulke） 曾經在香港扶輪社公開演講，提出城邦論。</span>此建議在英國2014年外交及聯邦事務部文件（FCO 40/1665 FUTURE OF HONG KONG）以及戴卓爾夫人的公開書信顯示。 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>然而，香港學界及政界並無反應，民主回歸論竟然成為主流。</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n//蘇偉澤其實構想的獨立香港是一種可稱為「沒有主權的獨立」（Independence without Sovereign）（看似矛盾？）： <span style=\"color: red;\">他認為香港獨立後仍可是中國的一部分，歷史上中歐的城市雖然獨立，但仍是屬於羅馬帝國的一部分。在他眼中，<strong>香港因歷史的緣故，已發展成異於中國和台灣，並具有強大經濟實力和獨特生活方式的城邦（city state）</strong></span>；而且早在1960年代，要不是中國因素的影響，香港早已經歷去殖化獨立，現在或已是聯合國和東南亞國家聯盟（ASEAN）的一員，同時具備經濟實力和政治影響力。但由於中方的反對，任何關於獨立的想法，無論是否挑戰主權的，以及基本的民主實踐如開放立法局選舉都被阻止。與其說他是港獨派，這裏面某些理解更似城邦派。// <br />\n<br />\n本研解密﹕被遺忘的「自決派」&mdash;&mdash;蘇偉澤（Walter M. Sulke） <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161127/s00005/1480184212715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161127%2Fs00005%2F1480184212715&d=qxVWWVIkSK%2BieYma0ob7LsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=0a92c7e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161127%2Fs00005%2F1480184212715&h=fbe1e538\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161127/s00005/1480184212715</a> <br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shares/view?id=10154683542812225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshares%2Fview%3Fid%3D10154683542812225&d=qxVWWVIkSK%2BieYma0ob7LsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=c3470935\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shares/view?id=10154683542812225</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nWan Chin   陳雲 《香港城邦論》其實是英國式的政治理論。故此與解密檔案相符，並不奇怪。"},{"pid":"526e408dc1f341457d34d6c020a82583b7834ed6","tid":9289,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"貼錯source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更正：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154683542812225&amp;id=589657224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10154683542812225%26id%3D589657224&d=qxVWWVIkSK%2BieYma0ob7LsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f2a3bd85\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154683542812225&amp;id=589657224</a>"},{"pid":"4e0e78312a920be7195d3d53fa13ee16ac48ef6e","tid":9289,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65f34bbd7ccd14f5121104600eac766d579395e","tid":9289,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"人地個城邦無講要建立華夏聯邦呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fd04d09ea6f5032f284772cb0790484c677152","tid":9289,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f80a6c67101c033f2ac2b390f064dfca7da9145","tid":9289,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地個城邦無講要建立華夏聯邦呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 係邦聯。唔該搞清楚聯邦同邦聯嘅分別<br />\n2. 咁先至說明陳雲嘅城邦論更加全面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{